  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/a1377696-373f-46f9-a3c8-571ed9edc8b6.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>策划了一个短途游，去Coromandel。上次去是4年前。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/a1377684-00d7-47b2-ba4b-32e716dd1f02.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>教堂湾那天天气很好，人也不少。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/a137765a-4fb9-466a-b923-793d0af84526.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>步道风景很好。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/a13776a5-53f6-4662-9224-615009411edb.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>路边的光影。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/a137743e-df71-44fa-941d-3c43d8c26e2d.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>晚上银河肉眼可见。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/a137744b-fc88-43b5-9a0c-831e0d4a3766.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
